readable.content: A man is parallel in the air , trying to kick the soccer ball past the goalie . a soccer player in white attacks the ball with flying kick towards the goal of the player in red as another team member looks on . A soccer player is jumping into the air to kick the soccer ball into the goal . A soccer player is making a flying kick towards the goal . A soccer player leaps sideways in the air to kick the ball .
